{"tid":1251743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警總滿布蛋漬 休班警自發到場打掃","createTime":"2019-06-22T16:16:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T16:47:58.000Z","uid":66271,"like":2,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b269d23f9d58e188b8812021152cdef00ea4f2ee","tid":1251743,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:16:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jkrgHlCpdfjvFKTijSLgvQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/onccinstantnews.com/e2ea24a88e67ee6c3ec9451ef2b0bba2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FjkrgHlCpdfjvFKTijSLgvQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2Fe2ea24a88e67ee6c3ec9451ef2b0bba2&h=4fe13628&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n修訂《逃犯條例》風波仍未平息，示威者昨日(21日)發起包圍灣仔警察總部，又向總部掟雞蛋。西區警區十多名休班警員，今日(22日)中午自發到警總外進行清理工作。他們用上漂白水、天拿水等，清洗扶手電梯污漬，又用地拖和抹布清理外牆上的蛋漬。"},{"pid":"d2f00be978141dbef35cf03d3fc54ceac361d85c","tid":1251743,"uid":103759,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:27:55.000Z","msg":"當當警察要做埋清潔姐姐果份 陰鳩功 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係呢 你哋個阿頭一哥呢 做咩唔落來一齊洗 佢好支持你哋嘅喎 <br />\n當年沙士政府高層都有落街做樣洗下街嘅喎"},{"pid":"9c836081c1fadbe3d4fd9909dcc8f39d15db7872","tid":1251743,"uid":194012,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:30:47.000Z","msg":"博升職<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n休班都咁撚勤力<br />\n遲吓比卡超都冇得做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c432ff168a41f1a6b872c094f7bd64845b1402","tid":1251743,"uid":130695,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T16:31:21.000Z","msg":"休班警犯完法 咪要出黎做下戲<br />\n陣間又震怒爆血管邊個睇住呢班警畜"},{"pid":"e026b9835a9717476b92d057c73ff4b782750b9b","tid":12